    "body": "eww... all these separate cases for windows are really getting annoying.  However, I'm not sure what else we can do.\n\nI'd love to change [parse_options](https://github.com/ipython/ipython/blob/master/IPython/core/magic.py#L604) to have `posix=True` by default instead of `posix = (os.name == 'posix')`.  That would fix many of the issues.\n"
